    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Wood frames for the support of canvas or other textile that do not have expandable corners. For similar frames having expandable corners, use "stretchers (framing and mounting equipment)."</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000000/VP</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000008491/Chieffo, Contemporary Oil Painter's Handbook (1976)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Marcos de madera que sostienen el lienzo u otro textil que no ha sido expandido hasta las esquinas. Para marcos similares que presentan cuñas, use "bastidor de cuñas".</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Spanish</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000131/CDBP-SNPC</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000051034/TAA database (2000-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Houten frames zonder verstelbare hoeken, die worden gebruikt voor het ondersteunen van canvas of ander textiel. Gebruik 'spanramen (benodigdheden voor inlijsten en monteren)' voor soortgelijke frames met verstelbare hoeken.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Dutch</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000205/AAT-Ned</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000113770/AAT-Ned (1994-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>用以支撐畫布或其他織品的木框，其四角不具延展性。若指四角具有延展性的類似框架，請參閱「畫布框 (鑲裝與裱貼設備)」。 </Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Chinese (traditional)</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000250/AS-Academia Sinica</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
